name: Spring Showers Bring Colorful Songbirds 01
description: The image, "Spring Showers Bring Colorful Songbirds 01" was created to depict the colorful eastern migratory songbirds of Spring. Many songbirds have been classified as "endangered" or "high risk for extinction" due to the increase in nest predation and invasive species as well as disappearing habitats through deforestation. The image was created with the assistance of artificial intelligence, VQGAN+CLIP (machine learning algorithms), and text prompts. The image may be interpreted differently through the eyes and imagination of the viewers.
